    "The correct report is present in the top ten reports 33.3% of the time.",
    "Going from text to image, the average rank of the matching video is 203 out of 21,484 and the correct video is present in the top ten ranked videos 34.3% of the time.",
    "For all language models, the choice of text prompts impacts model performance and we found EchoCLIP to be easier to generate focused prompts compared to EchoCLIP-R given the larger context for in-domain prompts (Table 2).",
    "A workflow for automated preliminary assessment of echocardiogram studies by ensembling assessments across videos is shown in the Supplementary Video.",
    "The ability to measure the similarity between pairs of echocardiograms can also be used to identify a unique patient across multiple studies (a difficult task for human clinicians) as well as identify clinical changes over time."
